dct_title_s: Map of the boundary line between the states of New York and New Jersey
dct_description_sm: Map of the boundary line between the states of New York and New Jersey in lands under water in Kill Von Kull and New York Bay, from the Baltimore and Ohio Bridge in Arthur Kill near Elizabethport, New Jersey to the Hudson River opposite the Battery, New York City.
